title: Futurama [Recapstore]
description:
(recapstore) Stephen Fry, a Pizza guy is sent to the Futurama after falling into a time machine. In the future, comedy ensues.

(imdb)Phillip Fry is a 25-year-old pizza delivery boy whose life is going nowhere. When he accidentally freezes himself on December 31, 1999, he wakes up 1,000 years in the future and has a chance to make a fresh start. He goes to work for the Planet Express Corporation, a futuristic delivery service that transports packages to all five quadrants of the universe. His companions include the delivery ship's captain, Leela, a beautiful one-eyed female alien who kicks some serious butt, and Bender, a robot with very human flaws.

Whichever way you would describe it, this torrent presents the entire 7 seasons in only 3.7gb, and that is the only true fact of the universe. Enjoy and seed!
